io.hekate.election

Class ElectionServiceFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.hekate.election.ElectionServiceFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceFactory<ElectionService>

    public class ElectionServiceFactory
extends Object
implements ServiceFactory<ElectionService>
    Factory for ElectionService.

    This class represents a configurable factory for ElectionService. Instances of this class can be registered within the HekateBootstrap in order to customize options of the ElectionService.

    For more details about the ElectionService and its capabilities please see the documentation of ElectionService interface.

    See Also:
    ElectionService
